ResponseRule.name: Power Plant: Hydrogen Leak -- TranScribe Version
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila contacts player to explain the danger of the leaking hydrogen gas. This is an alternate to the in person version.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila In Office, How to Reboot Station
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila is already in the player's office. She contacts the player in Life Support to let the player know how to open up the airlocks and lifts again by rebooting the station.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila in Power Plant, Already Met, How to Reboot Station
ResponseRule.description: Player has met Mikhaila, but has not yet brought her meds, so she's still in the power plant when the player is coming through to reboot the station.

ResponseRule.name: First Contact -- Plyr Helped Sec Chief
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila contacts player for the first time, as player is heading from Cargo Bay to Power Plant. Mikhaila knows player is on their way because they helped sec chief.

ResponseRule.name: First Contact -- Plyr Ditched Sec Chief
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila contacts player for the first time, as player is heading from Cargo Bay to Power Plant. In this case the player spoke to the Sec Chief Sara, but then opened the bay doors without helping her anyway (letting in hordes of aliens).

ResponseRule.name: First Contact -- Sec Chief Dead or Ignored
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila contacts player for the first time, as player is heading from Cargo Bay to Power Plant. In this case the player either ignored or killed the Sec Chief.

ResponseRule.name: Power Plant: Start
ResponseRule.description: Player arrived in the power plant. Mikhaila touches base again, trying to be helpful.

ResponseRule.name: Power Plant: Clue About Talia Brooks
ResponseRule.description: Player reached the coolant room but will need to find Talia Brooks' keycard to access Mikhaila and progress.

ResponseRule.name: Power Plant: Reactor Reboot Halted. Problems.
ResponseRule.description: Player investigates insde of the reactor and sees the busted diverter.

ResponseRule.name: Power Plant: Reboot Finished, Stuff is Broken Now - Sick
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila explains the ripple effects of rebooting the station reactor.

ResponseRule.name: Power Plant: Reboot Finished, Stuff is Broken Now
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila explains the ripple effects of rebooting the station reactor.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: Don't Worry About My Medicine
ResponseRule.description: This TranScribe occurs after the player has encountered Mikhaila and is headed toward her medicine (Mikhaila is assuming the player is risking their life to go get it).

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: Don't Worry About My Medicine, Stronger
ResponseRule.description: This TranScribe occurs after the player has encountered Mikhaila and is headed toward her medicine (Mikhaila is assuming the player is risking their life to go get it). Mikhaila is weaker now.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: Don't Worry About My Medicine, Last One
ResponseRule.description: This TranScribe occurs after the player has encountered Mikhaila and is headed toward her medicine (Mikhaila is assuming the player is risking their life to go get it). Mikhaila is much weaker now.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: Morgan Grabbed the Medicine
ResponseRule.description: This should not play if the player already got her medicine. This should be triggered right before/after player gets the boosters.

ResponseRule.name: Dead From Lack of Medicine
ResponseRule.description: Plyr Fixed the Reactor but hasn't yet visited or helped Mikhaila. Contacts him one last time. She dies shortly after.

ResponseRule.name: Reached Morgan's Office Alone
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila reached the player's office. This means the player helped her out by retrieving her medicine. She's the only one in the office.

ResponseRule.name: Reached Morgan's Office w/ January
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila reached the player's office. This means the player helped her out by retrieving her medicine. When she arrives, January floats in, startling her.

ResponseRule.name: Reached Morgan's Office w/ Igwe
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila reached the player's office. This means the player helped her out by retrieving her medicine. When she enters, Igwe says hello (to her irritation).

ResponseRule.name: Reached Morgan's Office w/ Igwe + Junuary
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila reached the player's office. This means the player helped her out by retrieving her medicine. Both Igwe and January are already there.

ResponseRule.name: Lobby: Dahl Arrived
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila calls to comment about the arrival of Dahl.

ResponseRule.name: Lobby: Dahl Arrived -- Mik Offers Help
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila calls to offer the player supplies / help.

ResponseRule.name: Lobby: Dahl Defeated
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila calls to comment about Dahl's defeat. This would only play if Igwe is dead. ***Avellone Note: Check this.***

ResponseRule.name: Lobby: Dahl Converted
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila calls to see what's up with Dahl. Should play sometime after the player leaves the Sim Labs and Dahl is converted. Basically, letting the player know that she is de-spawning form the office and headed to Shuttle Bay. Shouldn't play if Igwe or Dahl are dead.

ResponseRule.name: Lobby: Operators Are Breaking In
ResponseRule.description: Dahl's Operators are trying to cut their way into Morgan's office.

ResponseRule.name: Lobby: Operators Are Breaking In, More Urgent
ResponseRule.description: Dahl's Operators are trying to cut their way into Morgan's office. More Urgent follow up.

ResponseRule.name: Lobby: Operators Are Breaking In, We're Dead
ResponseRule.description: Dahl's Operators are trying to cut their way into Morgan's office. We're dead.

ResponseRule.name: Whistleblower Finished
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila gave plyr the Whistleblower objective and plyr just fnished it by finding the secret box of mementoes in the cargo bay (which matches Volunteer names to numbers).

ResponseRule.name: Deep Storage: Morgan Transfered Mik's Father's Log
ResponseRule.description: Player just uploaded Mikhaila's father's log. Mikhaila calls to verify.

ResponseRule.name: Deep Storage: Morgan Destroyed Mik's Father's Log
ResponseRule.description: Player just destroyed Mikhaila's father's log. Mikhaila calls to ask what's going on.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila's Father: Forgiveness. Thank You
ResponseRule.description: The player played the experiment log for Mikhaila which revealed her father's fate, and the player's guilt. Mikhaila has processed it a little and contacts the player to share her thoughts.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila's Father: Never Forgive You
ResponseRule.description: The player deleted Mikhaila's father's log right in front of her. She hates you, but will still communicate on anything critical to get off the station.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: Apex Arrival
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila calls to comment about the Apex arrival.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: Side With January. No Shuttle. No Igwe
ResponseRule.description: Player has probably placed the Null Wave and is headed back to the bridge. Mikhaila chimes in to try and peruade him away. After this, it's assumed that Mikhaila and January are in the same location, so if the player kills or disables January, he'll have to kill Mikhaila as well, and she won't be there for the victory.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: End Games. Pwnd Igwe. No Shuttle.
ResponseRule.description: Player is on his way to the bridge to trigger one of the final end-games and there is not a shuttle. Igwe, Mikhaila, and Jan are still alive.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: End Games. Player Has Both Keys. No Shuttle. TS Version
ResponseRule.description: Player picked up both keys and is on his way to the Power Plant.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: End Games. Player USED Both Keys. No Shuttle. TS Version
ResponseRule.description: Player USED both keys and is on his way to the Bridge.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: End Games. Final Fare Well. Escape Pod. No Shuttle. TS Version
ResponseRule.description: Player triggered self destruct and is on his way to escape pod (or sitting in the chair, prob works in either case).

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: Come to the Shuttle
ResponseRule.description: Player triggered self-destruct and survivors are ready to go in the Shuttle Bay.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: Come to the Shuttle, Last Warning
ResponseRule.description: Player triggered self-destruct and survivors are ready to go in the Shuttle Bay. Last warning.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: Final Goodbye, Morgan Staying.
ResponseRule.description: Final goodbye message.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: Mikhaila Stranded. Morgan Escape Pod.
ResponseRule.description: Player leaves, Mikhaila is alive (alone). BOOM. Station detonates.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: Mikhaila Saved. Alex Escape Pod.
ResponseRule.description: Just in case. Mikhaila saved by entering Alex's pod.

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: Mikhaila enters Morgan Office 1st Time, January Dead
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila reaches Morgan's office, January is lying dead on the floor (Mikhaila doesn't know how January died).

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: Mikhaila enters Morgan Office 1st Time, Igwe Dead
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila reaches Morgan's office, Igwe is lying dead on the floor (Mikhaila doesn't know how Igwe died).

ResponseRule.name: Mikhaila: Mikhaila enters Morgan Office 1st Time, January and Igwe Dead
ResponseRule.description: Mikhaila reaches Morgan's office, Igwe and January are both dead on the floor (Mikhaila doesn't know how either one of them died).
